#summary Overview of SSPxxx registers per PIC

----

= Overview of SSPxxx registers per PIC =

Based on MPLAB version 8.83

The names of the SSP registers are the 'raw' names from MPLAB.
Multi-bit fields are enumerated, like in the datasheets.
In the device files multi-bit fields are mostly declared as single variable!
<br>Double names (like D/NA, R/NW) are not splitted here.
